  "short_description": "Embody a tiny shroom and try to unite all of shroomkind before a massive storm sends everyone back to the mycelial age. Lead a crowd of cheery mushrooms and brawl through the islands. Bring peace, berries, and the peace of mycelium to every agaricus bisporus in the land!",
